 Von Teese]], a notable model, [[costume designer]], author, actress, singer, & entrepreneur *[[Kate Lambert|Kato]], a notable model, designer, & entrepreneur *[http://www.thealternativemodeldirectory.com The Alternative Model Directory], an online directory of alternative models from all over the globe.
